(56, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Request information', 'Published', 'request-information', 'en', 'Request information', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p>Our activities and events are available across the UK. To find out more about how we may be able to support the work you do, please contact your nearest Creation Station&nbsp;<a title="Arts Crafts provider" href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/Franchise-Map/">arts and crafts provider</a>.</p>\r\n<p>For national activities and events please contact <a href="mailto:partnership@thecreationstation.co.uk">partnership@thecreationstation.co.uk</a>&nbsp;and we will be in touch with you within 48 hours.<br />Thank you.</p>\r\n<p><a title="Group Events" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/group-events"><span style="color: #d70000;">Group Events&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #d70000;"><a title="Event Partners" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/who-we-work-with">Who We work with &gt;&gt;</a></span></p>\r\n<p><a title="What we do" href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/who-we-work-with"><span style="color: #d70000;">What do we do&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 35, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(57, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Franchise Support', 'Published', 'franchise-support', 'en', 'Franchise Support', '<p>Setting up your own business can be a daunting prospect for many. it''s one of the reasons that the tried and tested model of a successful franchise is so appealing to so many.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It''s not just the fact that the business works, but it&rsquo;s also because with the right franchise you receive a wealth of support and hand holding&nbsp; for the whole time you run your franchise.&nbsp;<br />Our franchisees state that they feel supported when they start out, as they grow their business, as is they start to get really established and need help with&nbsp; managing their successful business.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a title="childrens franchise" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt; Follow our blog and meet some of the Creative Hub team&nbsp;</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><video controls="controls" width="500" height="250">\r\n<source src="franchise-support" /></video></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 36, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(58, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Family Event Entertainer Feeback', 'Published', 'family-event-entertainer-feeback', 'en', 'Family Event Entertainer Feeback', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\r\n<p>We are proud to work with so many oraganistions acorss the&nbsp;U.K. who have the same shared passion for&nbsp;providing quality engaging creative family fun.</p>\r\n<p>Here''s what&nbsp;our partners have said about us:</p>\r\n<h3>Run the Kidszone for Olympics in Hyde park for 15 days</h3>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 10px;">&ldquo;The Creation Station team planned and delivered an exceptional kids zone for the children and family visitors to Hyde Park over the 15 days of the Games 2012. They organised everything and just got on and delivered a great experience&rdquo;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 10px;">Patrick Loy Organiser - Live Nation &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h3>Chessington World Of Adventure</h3>\r\n<p>"From proposal to execution Creation Station are the most passionate, almost too good to be true, company to work with.&nbsp; They provide innovative and thoroughly enjoyable activities and we have had nothing but praise from all our adventurers that have taken part in their themed activities.&nbsp; The Creation Station team seems constantly happy and motivated and is never too happy to go the extra mile, even in the highest pressure situations!&nbsp;Thanks"<br />&nbsp;<br />Sophie Cross<br />Marketing Manager<br />Holiday Inn Chessington <br />Chessington World of Adventures Resort.</p>\r\n<h3>Dutch Day in&nbsp;Trafalgar Square for 75,000 visitors</h3>\r\n<p>&ldquo;We were looking for somebody to keep thousands of children entertained over the afternoon with a range of activities, which had been tailored to suit our festival (and more importantly, my budget!).&nbsp; From my first point of contact with Creation Station&rsquo;s head office I knew I was going to be in good hands.&nbsp; They listened to what I needed, suggested ideas that might work better and were of great help when the inevitable problems that come with organising a festival for 70,000+ people reared their heads!&nbsp; On the actual day of the event, I felt confident leaving Kaio and her team to do what they do best.&nbsp; The overall response from families who visited Kaio and her art&rsquo;s and craft&rsquo;s corner was overwhelmingly positive, with lots of people praising the huge amount of patience she has!&nbsp; We will definitely be in touch next year&hellip;!&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>James Mill -MJR Tom</p>\r\n<h3>St Particks Parade in Trafalgar Square for 90,000 visitors</h3>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Having seen The Creation Station run the kidszone for the Olympics, we approached them to provide &nbsp;fun and engaging family event entertainment for &nbsp;our St Patrick day celebrations in Trafalgar square. They understood what we needed and provided a fun selection of themed arts and &nbsp;crafts activities to inspire our &nbsp;90,000 thousand visitors. When it was announced that there was no access to water, Creation Station solved the problem by adapting the themed activities at short notice. &nbsp;The feedback has been great and it&rsquo;s been a real pleasure working with The Creation Station team&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>D&aacute;ire Basra&nbsp;Senior Officer, Events for London. The Mayors Office&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Shopping Centres</h3>\r\n<p>"The Creation Station always do a fantastic job at Braehead, as they are consistently professional and very creative with their ideas for our craft workshops.&nbsp; The children have lots of fun and are always so happy with what they get to take home as a special keepsake from their time at Braehead."</p>\r\n<p>Braehead Shopping Centre Management, Scotland</p>\r\n<h3><span style="font-size: 19px;">County Shows</span></h3>\r\n<p>"The Creation Station provided a range of inspiring activities for our family zone and they also ran our Kids 4 fun zone over three days at the Devon County Show. We had over 100,000 visitors over the three days and the feedback from parents and children was that the activities were a huge hit. We have included Creation station in all our forthcoming shows as they add so much to the family experience"</p>\r\n<p>Devon County Show Organiser</p>\r\n<h3>Creative Fun in Shopping Centres</h3>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Meadowlane Shopping Centre is delighted to be associated with Creation Station. &nbsp;Our customers and their children really enjoy the weekly art sessions that are held here and it is fantastic to see the kids explore and experiment with so many different types of arts and crafts in a fun creative environment. &nbsp;We also use Creation Station for our seasonal and promotional events and they have always created a bespoke package of activities to suit our particular requirements and which also suits all age-groups of children. &nbsp;Creation Station carry out the events with a high level of enthusiasm, professionalism and customer service which is second to none and I couldn&rsquo;t recommend them highly enough.&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Sarah O''Neill Center Manager - Meadowlane Shopping Centre</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<a href="admin/admin/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></p>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 37, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(59, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Receive Your Free Info Pack', 'Published', 'receive-your-free-info-pack', 'en', 'Receive Your Free Info Pack', '<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<p>You are about to find out how this award winning and fastest growing childrens activity franchise could give you what you are looking for. Simply complete the form below and click submit then give us a call on <span id="skype_c2c_container" class="skype_c2c_container notranslate" dir="ltr" tabindex="-1" data-numbertocall="+441395239700" data-isfreecall="false" data-isrtl="false" data-ismobile="false"><span class="skype_c2c_highlighting_inactive_common" dir="ltr"><span id="non_free_num_ui" class="skype_c2c_textarea_span"><img class="skype_c2c_logo_img" src="chrome-extension://lifbcibllhkdhoafpjfnlhfpfgnpldfl/call_skype_logo.png" alt="" width="0" height="0" /><span class="skype_c2c_text_span">01395 239700</span></span></span></span> to book your "Discover Chat" with Maggie.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Over 80 women and men are already ready running their own inspiring Creation Station and demand for our award winning arts and crafts classes, parties, and events keeps increasing. So there really has never been a better time to look at investing in your own future.</p>\r\n<p>Please note that you do need to be able to drive to operate the Franchise and the investment level starts at &pound;5,500 plus Vat.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This opportunity isn''t right for everyone, so let''s have a chat first and see if this is something that could be right for you or not.</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Complete the form below and we will give you a call.</strong></h4>\r\n<p>I look forward to hearing from you,</p>\r\n<p>Sarah Cressall</p>\r\n<p>The Mum of The Creation Station</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 38, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(60, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'How to entertain children at weddings', 'Published', 'how-to-entertain-children-at-weddings', 'en', 'How to entertain children at weddings', '<div id="contentBlockLeft">\n<p>Firstly- if you are planning on gettin married congratulations to you both!&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Planning the big day is such an exciting activity and there are many things to&nbsp; plan, schedule, check and make decisions about.</p>\n<p>We all know that it is lovely to involve the family and include&nbsp;children in the special day too, but we also understand that those brilliant speeches just won&rsquo;t inspire the little ones in the same way as the older guests.</p>\n<p>That&rsquo;s why we have come up with a rather inspiring package that involves the children in the celebrations of the big day but allows them the opportunity to get enjoy getting creative too.&nbsp; If you would like to find out more about our <br />special bespoke &lsquo;Perfect Big Day For Little Ones Too&rsquo; package&nbsp; please email <a href="http://mce_hostmailto:weddingfun@thecreationstation.co.uk">weddingfun@thecreationstation.co.uk</a> and we will take care of this for you.</p>\n<p>Download Your Top 10 Tips on how to ensure children and their parents have a wonderful time at your wedding :)</p>\n<p>&gt;&gt; <a title="Top 10 Wedding Tips for entertaining children " href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/includes/documents/TopTenTipsthatwillhelpchildrenenjoyawedding.pdf" target="_blank" rel="external">Top 10 tips for entertaining children at your Wedding</a></p>\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 39, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(61, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Indoor entertainment', 'Published', 'indoor-entertainment', 'en', 'Indoor entertainment', '<h3>Discover how to increase footfall, retention and frequency of returning visitors with the fun and engaging activities provided by award winning Creation Station&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>The UK&rsquo;s leading creative experience company The Creation Station works with proactive family focussed organisations who provide exceptional experiences to their guests and support the local community but sometimes struggle with;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Extending the range of innovative fun activities on offer to attract a mixed age range of children in a family&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Developing new initiatives to bring in new customers to their centres</li>\r\n<li>Finding the time to develop and deliver, themed and seasonal activities to ensure guests are inspire to keep returning&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We help by working with individual organisations to help identify key challenges and to support with bespoke solutions.&nbsp;Some example of how The Creation can help include;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Increasing footfall by providing weekly art and crafts classes for children.</li>\r\n<li>Providing themed activities such as summer holiday fun, Halloween Christmas and Easter workshops and drop in fun.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Developing promotional and launch &nbsp;activities for your centre</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Find out how your centre can benefit from The Creation Station sensation. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;To find out more email our Creative Hub head Office on hello@thecreationstation.co.uk or <a title="Nearest Creation Station " href="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/franchise-map/" target="_blank" rel="external">click here to find your nearest Creation Station&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></p>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 40, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(62, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Baby classes', 'Published', 'baby-classes', 'en', 'baby-classes', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\r\n<div id="contentBlockLeft"><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/f8VKkb8Tj44&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" height="344" width="425" /></object>\r\n<h3>Baby discovery is&nbsp;a unique baby learning &amp; development experience with inspiring creative play &amp; treasured artworks.</h3>\r\n<p>We believe this is the ultimate&nbsp;creative journey of discovery for your baby. Share the experience of fun&nbsp;hands-on learning - the sort of stuff you wouldn''t do at home - in a&nbsp;safe and&nbsp;nurturing environment. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Plus, make special&nbsp;artworks&nbsp;with your baby to take home, play with and treasure for ever.</p>\r\n<p>What will you and your baby discover today?</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>An educational programme that supports your baby''s learning and development</li>\r\n<li>Hands-on, fun, shared experiences&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>The joy of exploring and developing new sensations together</li>\r\n<li>Safe and nurturing development activities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br />You&rsquo;ll also help your baby create their first art work and other treasured pieces and discover more of the world around them.</p>\r\n<p>Classes include a wealth of art and crafts materials and what you make is yours to take home. Siblings are also welcome at a special big sister or big brother rate.</p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 10px;">Places are limited so contact your local Creation Station for more details.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a href="http://crm.checksample.co.uk/contact"><img src="http://www.thecreationstation.co.uk/images/structure/img_enquire-brush.png" alt="Enquire here" /></a></div>\r\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 41, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0),
(65, 0, 1, 4, 0, 'Become a franchise', 'Published', 'become-a-franchise', 'en', 'Become a franchise', '<div id="content" class="clearfix">\n<div id="contentBlockLeft"><object width="425" height="344"><embed src="http://youtube.com/v/0TSLYWAbsNE&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" width="425" height="344" /></object>\n<h4><strong><span style="line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 10px;">These pages are here to help you discover whether running your own Creation Station is the opportunity you have really been looking for.</span></strong></h4>\n<p>These are not&nbsp; &lsquo;sales'' pages, as we know the importance of finding the right people to join our team to deliver our values and share our passion about inspiring imaginations.</p>\n<p>Please take a look at each page on the site. We''ve tried to structure it so that you get an accurate picture of the opportunity.</p>\n<p>Our growing network of franchisees all came on board with different backgrounds - you can read how Lou wanted a flexible working, Ali needed a rewarding&nbsp;work life balance, and these stories are very inspiring.</p>\n<p><a title="Best opportunities" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">&gt;&gt; Follow our Best Creative Opportunities Blog to keep up to date with new stories and offers</a></p>\n<p>You will see many comments from Mums, Dads and organisations&nbsp;on the website, about how they have benefitted from the Creation Station, so you know that this product works!</p>\n<p>Then there''s the about us section. We think this is important that you have all the details about us and what are values are. We are committed to ensuring we&nbsp;comply with the highest standards of&nbsp;best practise, to provide a professional, fair and ethical&nbsp;business for all our franchsiees.&nbsp;&nbsp;This&nbsp;demonstrates that we can be trusted to get it right, to work closely with you and to go the extra mile when it comes to guiding, supporting and assisting you, if you''re right for this business and you come on board with us. <br /><br />So enjoy having a browse and finding out about our business - and what it could be like as your business - and don''t forget to book in your "Discover Chat"</p>\n<p>In the meantime, if you''ve any questions give us a call&nbsp;or&nbsp;send us an email&nbsp;and we''ll be happy to answer them for you.</p>\n<p>Call Maggie on &nbsp;01395 239700</p>\n<p>or email;&nbsp; <a href="http://mce_hostmailto:franchise@thecreationstation.co.uk">franchise@thecreationstation.co.uk</a></p>\n<p>You may find the following link to our blog helpful too;</p>\n<h4><strong>&gt;&gt;&nbsp;<a title="Best Opportunities" href="http://bestcreativeopportunities.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="external">Discover what happens behind the scenes and true life stories of franchise owners</a></strong></h4>\n</div>\n</div>', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 0, 0, 44, '1', 0, 1, 0, 0);
